If you use the Platform on your mobile device, we may collect data about your device.
Log information
Details of your use of the Platform including technical information such as traffic data, weblogs.
Location information
We collect data indicating your location while you are using the Platform.
Information we receive from other sources
We are working closely with third parties (including, for example, the Gaelic Athletic Association. We also work with equivalent other sports governing bodies depending on the relevant sport.
